  "2349630": {
    "name": "古镇闲居",
    "steam_appid": 2349630,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方QQ群号：151131724</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/5a6ab92af37ccc3a5c844722204d3972.avif?t=1757990353\" width=500 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款玩法丰富、细节满满的慢节奏写实风种田游戏，想要满足你所有的种田幻想！古镇围绕著一颗数百年的荔枝树而建，故名为荔枝镇，流行着你热爱的传统&amp;现代文化，新生活从这里开启。游戏玩法不止如此，更多的惊喜等待你去挖掘！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/9f67c22a3dfb957dce9fe6c5ffb35646.webp?t=1757990353\" width=600 height=60 /></span>——古色古香的中式小镇，熟悉的街道、建筑、店铺等</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——体验传统节日氛围，例如春节、元宵节等会有特定的场景</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——丰富的中国传统文化：例如国风服饰、茶文化、烹饪、油纸伞、灯笼等</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——探索传统中国美食的制作</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/f02b8a932b9b2bc673caf623d9a68117.poster.avif?t=1757990353\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/f02b8a932b9b2bc673caf623d9a68117.webm?t=1757990353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/f02b8a932b9b2bc673caf623d9a68117.mp4?t=1757990353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/d08d9536e15f2309f4a40902ae201c26.poster.avif?t=1757990353\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/d08d9536e15f2309f4a40902ae201c26.webm?t=1757990353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/d08d9536e15f2309f4a40902ae201c26.mp4?t=1757990353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/71e6d6153b345b4d0fa6e84011925fa3.webp?t=1757990353\" width=600 height=60 /></span>——清理荒地，开垦田地，制作农具，修建最适合自己风格的农场</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——数十种农作物，体验从种子种下到成熟收成的全过程</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——数十种花卉，种花爱好者的天堂</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——显著的四季变化，不同季节有不同景象，可挑选当季的作物种植</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——饲养包括鸡、鸭、鹅、猪、兔、鹌鹑等多种动物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/8aed29131e21a49e144b40f7c49d1827.poster.avif?t=1757990353\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/8aed29131e21a49e144b40f7c49d1827.webm?t=1757990353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/8aed29131e21a49e144b40f7c49d1827.mp4?t=1757990353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/e8b314bad6926525490b46cf3fd0c25c.poster.avif?t=1757990353\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/e8b314bad6926525490b46cf3fd0c25c.webm?t=1757990353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/e8b314bad6926525490b46cf3fd0c25c.mp4?t=1757990353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/2d86efe8a02e9e7cec12f86df31913c9.webp?t=1757990353\" width=600 height=60 /></span>——DIY装扮自己的农场以及小屋</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——丰富的主角装扮，各种风格应有尽有</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——古镇超过30位居民，你可以和他们结交、闲聊、游玩，探索奇妙的人际关系</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——10余位单身居民可深入交往，发展恋爱关系，甚至组建家庭，共同打理农场</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——还有不少流浪动物，抚摸它们给它们吃的，它们可能就会跟你成为好朋友跟你回家</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/30daab9d51cb0ec73370d970a23bef7e.poster.avif?t=1757990353\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/30daab9d51cb0ec73370d970a23bef7e.webm?t=1757990353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/30daab9d51cb0ec73370d970a23bef7e.mp4?t=1757990353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/f65225d6b30cf9e6a7338ff7536f90ee.avif?t=1757990353\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras_big/f65225d6b30cf9e6a7338ff7536f90ee.avif?t=1757990353 width=800 height=1792 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/db89b0cb0392127718c5966586140233.webp?t=1757990353\" width=600 height=60 /></span>——周边由丰富的自然景观可探索，竹林、树林、海滩等，可采集有特色的植物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——野外爬坡、游泳、钓鱼等，周围的水域生活着超过40种季节性鱼类</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——有机会偶遇国宝大熊猫，触碰意想不到的惊喜！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——神秘的矿洞探索，获取珍贵的物品，还可制作有趣武器打败矿洞的守卫</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/198597ee968e0a979e15d8ceb414a8d0.poster.avif?t=1757990353\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/198597ee968e0a979e15d8ceb414a8d0.webm?t=1757990353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2349630/extras/198597ee968e0a979e15d8ceb414a8d0.mp4?t=1757990353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
